***Student Results Manager***

A smart, faculty-first web application to analyze student exam results — instantly rank students, detect backlogs, and generate analytics from any file format.
Student Results Manager is a React-based tool built for teachers and academic coordinators. After uploading a result sheet (CSV, Excel, or university PDF), the application 
automatically parses the data, ranks every student by SGPA/CGPA, flags who has backlogs, and presents it all in a clean analytics dashboard — no manual processing needed.
Whether you're checking who failed, counting pending subjects, or comparing branch-wise performance, this tool gives you answers in seconds.

 Features
